parameters:
What a massive oni! It's the first time I've seen one taller
than a watchtower!

I've never seen such a gigantic oni either! Those red
horns... could it be one of the battle oni...!?

That's right, Momiji-san. You left the Hachiwan Battle Oni,
didn't you? To fill your vacancy, I've spent over ten years
raising this oni. His name is [Kumokai Oni Nyuudou].
Mwahaha! I'll pluck your lives away!

Show yourself with dignity! Even if you're in disguise, I
can tell!
Grrrgh! My robe--! You brat, gah...!!
A cyclops oni!? Could it be, this gigantic oni is...?

Yes, that's the oni I've been searching for all this time.
The one who killed my family... I've finally found him. He's
my prey. Everyone else, stand back.

Grrrgh! I hate bright lights, that's why I wore the robe...
How dare you slash it to pieces? I won't forgive this!

The one who won't be forgiven is you! Do you remember? The
name of the village in Koshu called [Yugiri Village]--

Yes! The village you ravaged ten years ago! For my family
and the villagers' grudge, I'll make sure you never attack
anyone again by killing you here and now!

Hahaha. Nyuudou is no ordinary oni. To maintain that huge
body, he needs to consume at least thirty humans a montha
special oni that can't possibly remember the names and
number of grains of rice he's eaten.

You bastard! Are you trying to insult me, my family, and the
villagers!?

Ah, but I do remember. The girl who bravely challenged
Nyuudou barehanded--you were torn apart by his claws and
fell into the river. I thought you were dead, but
miraculously you survived, didn't you?
...! What? You were at Yugiri Village ten years ago too!?

Yes. I apologize for burning down the village without
permission. It was an oversight on my part for not being
able to control Nyuudou. But to think you're now seeking
revenge, how quaint... If you think you can win just because
you've learned ninjutsu, you're foolish.

~~~~! Don't mock me with your words! I will give you
absolute death right here!

Huhuhuhu. Will things really go so smoothly for you?
Attempting revenge could lead to being counterattacked.
Let's see how much power that powerless girl from ten years
ago has gained.

~~~~!? (His muscles are even thicker than before!? His
movements are incomparably faster--!?)

The gift of human nutrition. The more he eats, the stronger
he becomes. Other oni eat to maintain their life force, but
Nyuudou is different. He grows by consuming humans.
We won't let that happen. Of course, we will fight as well.

Don't rush in alone, Yugiri! We are here with you! You are
never alone!

Masaki-chan is right. It's different from 10 years ago. Now
we have comrades. If that cyclops is Yugiri-chan's enemy,
then as her comrades, it's our enemy too--let's defeat it
together.

Karin... I'm sorry... As a ninja, I lost my composure.
Thank you.

My, my. If the four of you are going to fight together, then
I have no choice but to join the battle. Nyuudou, go ahead
and rampage all you want. Show these presumptuous girls the
hammer of justice.
Grrraaaahhh!! I'll kill all four of you together!!
Bring it on! All of us will be your opponents--!

Guhahh!! (What is this sword!? My regeneration can't keep
up!)

----!! (Could it be... that sword is an ancient demon-
slaying sacred artifact...!? )
We won't give you a moment's respite! Ei--!
Guaaah! Damn it!! My leg tendons--!
It's time for a follow-up attack! Eat my foxfire, cyclops!

Yes! I learned the dual-wielding technique in the Iga ninja
group all for this moment--!

Iga ninja leader, Yugiri--I stake everything on this
barrage!

One sword carries my grudge--the other carries the grudge of
my family and the people of Yugiri Village who were killed
by you!
You did it, Yugiri-chan. You've finally avenged them.

Ah... Karin, Momiji-dono, Masaki-dono. It's all thanks to
everyone. Thank you so much. Now my long-standing grudge has
been cleared.

Ouch... What detestable humans and foxes you are. To think
you would defeat Nyuudou, whom I've been nurturing for
decades.

Your turn is next, Gyouon! You may have set fire to the
castle tower, but with this, the evil deeds of the demons
are over!

Haha! How amusing! It seems there's been a misunderstanding?
Did you think we were about to attack your castle tower?

We were just about to head back now that our business is
done. We've already taken the life of the shogunate's
highest authority long ago.

We're too late! Did our reinforcements fail to arrive in
time!?

If you doubt it, hurry up and check by climbing the castle
tower. Now, if you'll excuse me. I must prepare to show the
world of humans the greatest feast.
Wait, wait! We won't let you escape!

That sword, it's a divine weapon for fighting demons, isn't
it? From our perspective, it's quite a dangerous weapon. But
can you really defeat all 1000 of my subordinates with that
treasured blade?

It'll be a piece of cake! I'll cut them all down! Prepare
yourself!

Heh heh. It won't go like it did five years ago when your
father interfered.

Though we lost Nyuudou, the Edo castle is ablaze--our plan
has succeeded. The next time we meet, I will make sure to
give you a taste of hellish suffering. Farewell--

(...! Interfered five years ago...? Does that guy also know
about Dad?)
Regrettable... It seems we've let him escape...
A ritual, you say? What on earth is Gyouon plotting?

We must hurry to the top floor of the castle tower at once!
We need to check on the safety of our lord and the others!
Yes! Masane-san must be there too! Let's hurry!
